name: Terareum [OLD]
public_notice: Terareum has recently migrated from their old contract to a new one. Visit this post for more information and visit the new token page here.
additional_notices:
The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.
